OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has set out a
OL,7,Ftimetable for his departure as prime
OL,8,Fminister, as potential successor Andy
OL,9,FBurnham returns to Westminster.
OL,11,FStarmer appeared to get emotional as
OL,12,Fhe thanked his wife, Victoria, for her
OL,13,Fsupport, saying being prime minister
OL,14,Fwas the "proudest moment of my life".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
