PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FAs part of his speech, Starmer said
OL,7,Fthe question being asked is "whether I
OL,8,Fam best placed to lead us into the
OL,9,Fnext general election?" - and the
OL,10,Fanswer given by the parliamentary
OL,11,Fparty has led him to "resign as leader
OL,12,Fof the Labour Party".
OL,14,FStarmer has faced increasing pressure
OL,15,Fon his political future over the past
OL,16,Ffew months, with more than 100 Labour
OL,17,FMPs calling for him to vacate Number
OL,18,F10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FLess than two years after steering
OL,7,FLabour to a landslide General Election
OL,8,Fvictory, Starmer's premiership is
OL,9,Fcoming to an end. He will leave
OL,10,FDowning Street as the second shortest-
OL,11,Fserving Labour prime minister in
OL,12,Fhistory.
OL,14,FThe opening of his statement competed
OL,15,Fwith a protester outside Downing
OL,16,FStreet playing the EU anthem,
OL,17,FBeethoven's Ode To Joy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
