CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FAfter winning the Makerfield by-
OL,7,Felection, Burnham will be sworn in as
OL,8,Fthe Greater Manchester constituency's
OL,9,FMP, and Starmer has now appeared to
OL,10,Fhave cleared the way for Burnham's bid
OL,11,Fto become the UK's seventh PM in a
OL,12,Fdecade.
OL,14,FStarmer said he would do all he could
OL,15,Fto ensure an "orderly" transition of
OL,16,Fpower and that he had asked Labour's
OL,17,Fgoverning body to set out a timetable
OL,18,Fto replace him.
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FThe timetable is expected to begin on
OL,7,FJuly 9 and end by the summer recess to
OL,8,F"ensure a new leader is in place
OL,9,Fbefore Parliament returns in
OL,10,FSeptember".
OL,12,FThe King is expected to see Starmer at
OL,13,Ftheir weekly audience later this week,
OL,14,Fit is understood.
OL,16,FThey usually meet on Wednesdays for
OL,17,Fthe regular meeting to discuss
OL,18,Fgovernment matters following Prime
OL,19,FMinister's Questions, with the
OL,20,Fconversation usually taking place face
OL,21,Fto face.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
