OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FIn his resignation speech, Starmer
OL,7,Flooked back at Labour's first return
OL,8,Fto government in 14 years ` describing
OL,9,Fthe moment as "a page in our country's
OL,10,Fhistory turned after years of
OL,11,Fdisappointment and despair".
OL,13,F"The chance to change the lives of
OL,14,Fmillions of people for the better,
OL,15,Fthat's what I came into politics for
OL,16,Fthe journey to that point was not
OL,17,Feasy," he added.
OL,19,F"Six years ago, I inherited a Labour
OL,20,FParty that was politically,
OL,21,Ffinancially, and morally bankrupt.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,F"I was told time and time again that
OL,7,Fmy party was finished, that we were
OL,8,Fconsigned to history, that a majority
OL,9,Fat the general election, let alone a
OL,10,Flandslide majority, was impossible,
OL,11,Fbut we proved those people wrong."
OL,13,FIn his speech, he said that he will
OL,14,Fgive his "full and unequivocal
OL,15,Fsupport" to his successor, "knowing
OL,16,Fthat they will inherit a Britain that
OL,17,Fis far stronger and fairer than the
OL,18,Fone I inherited two years ago, better
OL,19,Fprepared for the challenges ahead, and
OL,20,Fbetter able to ensure the Labour Party
OL,21,Fsecures a second term in office".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
