OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782161281
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer steps down as Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FMeanwhile, London Mayor Sir Sadiq Khan
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to Starmer as "a man of
OL,8,Fgreat integrity" as he urged the prime
OL,9,Fminister's successor to "invest in
OL,10,Fevery part of the country" ` including
OL,11,Fthe capital.
OL,13,FPresident of the European Commission
OL,14,FUrsula von der Leyen also paid tribute
OL,15,Fto the outgoing Starmer - saying "It
OL,16,Fcan take many leaders to grow into the
OL,17,Fstatesman you became in just two years.
OL,19,F"European and Ukrainian security is
OL,20,Fstronger because of you.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@PO]qD@YOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
